name: all of us steve jobs 1
description: In my opinion, each of us humans, animals, objects, etc...have entered the game of life with a background story and we are playing our roles .Sometimes our roles change and sometimes we wish we could play eachothers roles. The Chess Room  I made symbolizes the game of life and the main element that I call "us" can be any of us entering the game of life with different clothes and faces as a sign of our uniqueness. This set is made of 2022 pieces and 33 pieces of  These characters are golden and will be sold at a higher price. Each of us can make our own role in the game of life !!!
